	<item>
		<title>冬天的胃病夏天怎么治（冬季易胃寒5种食物别碰！）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/10803.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 28 Jul 2023 05:21:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[水果百科]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[冬季]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[症状]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[胃寒]]></category>
